ggsjj_am_0039_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"职业粉尘","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"大气污染","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"蛋白酶-抗蛋白酶失调","fourth":"感染","answerPic":"","first":"吸烟"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，男，25岁。因外出春游至植物园，出现咳嗽、咳痰伴喘息1天入院。喘息貌，口唇发绀，在肺部可闻及广泛哮鸣音。医疗诊断是支气管哮喘，下面哪种是控制症状的首选药","discription":"当哮喘发作时，β<sub>2</sub>受体激动药是控制症状的首选药，如沙丁胺醇。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0051_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"β<sub>2</sub>受体激动药","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"色甘酸钠","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"α受体激动药","fourth":"氯苯那敏","answerPic":"","first":"氨茶碱"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，男，45岁。患颈部蜂窝织炎，颈部肿胀明显，应特别注意观察","discription":"颈部蜂窝织炎可引起喉头水肿并导致呼吸困难，压迫气管。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0167_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"体温","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"神志","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"吞咽","fourth":"血压","answerPic":"","first":"呼吸"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"初产妇，27岁，妊娠40周，阵发性腹痛10小时，宫缩10～15分钟1次，持续30秒，宫口开大2cm。此临床表现的原因是","discription":"临产时正常宫缩应持续30秒，间歇期为5～6分钟，该产妇表现为子宫收缩节律性异常。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0184_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"子宫收缩对称性异常","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"子宫收缩极性异常","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"腹肌和膈肌收缩力异常","fourth":"子宫收缩缩复作用异常","answerPic":"","first":"子宫收缩节律性异常"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"孕妇，31岁，妊娠38周。因阴道持续性流液2小时入院。医生诊断办胎膜早破，护士协助其采用的卧位应为","discription":